content: I do not have exact information on the latest acceptance rate for the medical school program at ucla. however, according to us news and world report rankings 2022, ucla's david geffen school of medicine has an acceptance rate of 2.4% for the 2020-2021 academic year, which is highly competitive. it is important to note that acceptance rates can vary from year to year and depend on various factors such as the number of applicants, qualifications, and resources available.
